&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Electrical Engineering, Computer Engineering, Robotics, or a related technical field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of full-cycle people management experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep technical expertise with CUDA, GPU parallel computing, and inference optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
